<sect1 id="dir_1a83b528599da40ca3e2005a9bc9336b_1autotoc_md121">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides lightweight, system-agnostic data types that describe interactions between entities. These types are consumed by the combat, health, and scoring subsystems without introducing coupling between them.</para>
</sect1>
